<plot>This show was the reenactment of the OJ Simpson Civil Trial held in Santa Monica by E! Entertainment Television. They would reenact, using actors, verbatim transcripts of what had transpired in the court the day prior. The court would not allow cameras into the courtroom. The shoot was a one camera shot from beginning till the end of the scene.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?579820</url></doc>
